headline.print_headline: Nicaragua Rescue Crews Find Capsized Boat
headline.main: Nicaragua Rescue Crews Find Capsized Boat

lead_paragraph: Rescue crews in Nicaragua have found a fishing boat that capsized in the Caribbean last week with 50 people aboard and are searching for 18 crew members who remain missing, authorities said Sunday.
